{
  "name": "Darkness",
  "type": "spell",
  "img": "icons/magic/unholy/orb-rays-blue.webp",
  "system": {
    "itemKey": "",
    "description": "<p>You create a 2 Space Sphere of Darkness within range.</p><p><strong>Relocate:</strong> When you Sustain this Spell or by spending 1 AP, you can move the Sphere up to 5 Spaces to another Space within range.</p><p><strong>Attach:</strong> When you cast the Spell, you can attach it to an object or creature within range. If you do, the target sheds Darkness in a 1 Space Aura and you can no longer use Relocate.</p><p>If the target is not willing, make a Spell Check against the target’s Agility Save. <strong>Check Success:</strong> The target becomes the source of the Darkness.</p><p><em><strong>System Tip:</strong> This item is configured to always roll Spell Check. Ignore MCP if you won't use this spell check.</em></p><p></p><p><span style=\"text-decoration: underline;\"><strong><span style=\"text-decoration: underline;\">Spell Enhancements</span></strong></span></p><p><strong>Range: (1 AP, Repeatable) </strong>The range of the Spell increases by 5 Spaces. You can use this Enhancement a maximum of two times.</p><p><strong>Area: (1 MP, Repeatable)</strong> The diameter of the Sphere increases by 1 Space.</p><p><strong>Duration: (1 MP, Repeatable)</strong> The duration increases by 1 step (10 min → 1 hour → Long Rest).</p><p><strong>Light Eater: (1 AP)</strong> Non-magical light sources within the area are extinguished.</p><p><strong>Grasping Gloom: (1 MP)</strong> When a creature enters the area for the first time on its turn or starts its turn there, it makes an Agility Save against your Save DC. <strong>Save Failure:</strong> The target is Slowed for 1 round.</p>",
